data.description: Gorgeously remodeled 3 bed, 2 bath home on the corner of main street in Hamilton! Breathetaking, park like back yard with a wood deck that you only see in magazines helps anchor this impeccable property. Inside every room is very large, centered around an open ktichen and dining with granite counters and a wonderful peninsula. Natural light beams through the bay windows in the dining room and spreads to the living room which has a wonderful WBFP, real wood trim, and soaring ceilings found throughout. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet + his and her closets that lead into a SPA LIKE ensuite bath featuring a beautifully subway tiled, double head shower overlooking the tub and a double vanity you will love. Must be seen to appreciate this one.  Two more bedrooms are found in the house, another is ensuite and perfect for guests or extended family stays.  Trees cover the property front to back and the gorgeous grass is irrigated by a 10 zone sprinkler system. Too much to list, CALL TODAY!
